## Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Follow mobile-first approach
- Use responsive utilities consistently:
  - `sm:` (640px) - Small devices
  - `md:` (768px) - Medium devices
  - `lg:` (1024px) - Large devices
  - `xl:` (1280px) - Extra large devices
  - `2xl:` (1536px) - 2X large devices

## shadcn/ui
- Use shadcn/ui components as base
- Extend components with Tailwind utilities
- Keep styles modular and reusable
- Use proper component variants

## Responsive Design
- Start with mobile layout first
- Test layouts across all breakpoints
- Use flexible units (rem, em, %)
- Implement proper touch targets (min 44x44px)
- Consider mobile navigation patterns
- Optimize for different screen sizes
